name: 1985 Record Breaker Ivan de Jesus - thr33smas Insert - #3MAS9
description:
The Ninth Day of thr33smas

Ninth card in a series of 12 cards looking back at the highlights of the first 7 months of thr33som3s mints.

While celebrating Decorative Gourd Season, thr33som3s crafted a mystery narrative throughout the paintings and descriptions of the Gourd Inserts.   Shayna Twitchell had gone missing, and the resolution of her disappearance and the subsequent indictment of a suspect were left to the members of the Grotto.

After weeks of clues and a final decision on a number of suspects and scenarios, the Grotto decided to indict Subs Shortstop Ivan de Jesus for the murder of Shayna Twitchell.

This card represents the hitting achievements of de Jesus during his time awaiting his murder trial.

The 12 Days of thr33smas is a chase 3v3nt. Collect all 12, #3MAS1 through #3MAS12, in the announced timeframe to receive #3MAS13 via airdrop.

This card is an INSERT. It has all established Standard Insert Utility and may compound additional Utilities over time. It is a Painting Insert, a thr33smas Insert and a Holiday Insert. ***** digital capture of original painting, gouache on vintage baseball card, 2021. ************ NFT image is for personal use, no commercial rights are granted.
